name: The Primordial Record
summary: Rowan kuranes awoke in a new world inside the body of a dying prince. His new body contain terrifying secrets that he has to protect, for inside him lies the key to Eternity.Rowan must learn to harness his new abilities and fight against his enemies who would stop at nothing to deprive him of his powers.Yet he must strive to keep a portion of his humanity alive, as he continously evolve beyond godhood.A/N: There are horror element, including Eldritch Horror from Lovecraft. Fan of blood borne, and abominable horrors that goes bump in the night would love it.Epic action set pieces, and galaxy wide battles, with an extremely overpowered MC who is a one man army. â¦â¦â¦â¦â¦â¦â¦â¦â¦â¦â¦â¦â¦â¦â¦â¦â¦â¦â¦â¦â¦â¦â¦
